divs: Sighting Detailsi was photographing some boats for my job and while sorting though the photos came across an interesting object in the middle top right corner of the picture. This is the original. I ran it though a photo editing program and looked at it as a negative and sharpened it to try to get a clearer view of it, but I am still unsure what it might be. I did not notice anything while taking the picture and only came across it while sorting through it and many other pictures. There are other pictures of that area from differnet angles but none have anything like it in them.
